1. Installed NVM using:
   curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash

2. Closed the terminal using: exit
   Reopenend the terminal to load NVM

3. Installed Node.js version 20.16.0 using:
   nvm install 20.16.0

4. Set Node.js 20.16.0 as default:
   nvm alias default 20.16.0

5. Verfied installation using:
   node -v
   npm -v

6. Installed SASS version 3.7.4 using:
   npm i sass@3.7.4
